sub_title: Owner of Art of Transports LLC
summary:
Hi, My Name is Ms. Dominique Johnson, and I am the Owner of Art of Transports LLC, hailing from North Louisiana. Family and Legacy are two words that I firmly believe in. I have a daughter and my main goal is to show her that in life, with hard work, consistency and drive you can create a legacy not only for you but for your family. I have a degree in Logistics and manufacturing and hold multiple Certifications including: Inventory control Technician,  Production Process Technician, Freight Broker, and Dispatch. I also hold a Class A commercial driver's license with no restriction and the following endorsements: Double/Triple Trailer, Hazardous Material, and Tanker.

With my extensive history within the trucking industry, I can assure that your business will be handled with the utmost care. I want to create the opportunities of education and employment to those in search of a legal and profitable career in the transportation/logistics industry. This is my life’s passion and purpose so I handle it with compassion, dedication, determination, understanding and most importantly faith. Faith that I can improve poverty one truck at a time. 

You master the “Art”, you master the industry and with great success I strive to ensure I do exactly that!!

education.field_of_study: Logistics, Materials, and Supply Chain Management

profile_positions.description: The Art of Transports LLC simply provides high-quality services to our valued clients by removing the guesswork out of the necessary requirements to successfully, and within compliance, start a career in the trucking transportation industry as an entrepreneur. Our team goes above and beyond to efficiently cater to each client’s specific needs. Through open communication and exceptional service, our vision is that you’ll find what you’re looking for with our company to start a life changing career journey.
